Neonatal Fc Receptor Binding Tolerance toward the Covalent Conjugation of 
Payloads to Cysteine 34 of Human Albumin Variants.

Petersen SS(1)(2), Kläning E(1)(2), Ebbesen MF(1)(2), Andersen B(3), Cameron 
